title: Leslie Jones
description:
Comedian Leslie Jones could give a sh*t if she was Conan O’Brien’s friend.

 

Leslie sits down with Conan to discuss her new podcast The Fckry, writing stand-up to fit her style, the lost art of accountability, and who at SNL she was secretly in love with. Later, Conan and his crew play sleuth to validate a dubious listener voicemail.

 

Got a question for Conan? Call our voicemail: (323) 451-2821.
 

For Conan videos, tour dates and more visit TeamCoco.com.
